fields.description:
Sourctree could not succesfully login to mercurial server running on adress
{{http://yourserver.net:5678/scm/hg/YOUREPO}}
When I tried to clone repositary, I was asked for username and password. When I inserted them, I was asked again and again. 

Problem was fixed with hand-editing of userhost config file in SourceTree directory in YourHome/AppData/Local/Atlassian/SourceTree/userhost.
I have to change the first line from this:
{{yourserver.net}}
to this
{{yourserver.net:5678}}

After this login was successfull. This problem was encountered also by all collegues.

I quess that problem is caused by different port which we are using. :)
